attributes.content: Amiya, take the Doctor with you.
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: Surely, you can feel it as well! She... If you don't leave, the entire rescue team will die here!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: She is a living monster! Amiya!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: We'll be fine, as long as we stand together!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: What about the Doctor, then? Can you ensure the Doctor's safety?
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: Team E4, we will stay behind and hold the line!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: We must ensure that Amiya, Dr {@nickname}, and the Medic teams escape safely!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: No, my squad will handle this.
attributes.name: Ace

attributes.content: Ace! Be rational, now's not the time to argue over this!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: Surely you can see it as well - everything around her is melting!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: I'm not going to leave you all here to fight alone.
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Amiya, time is of the essence! You have to escape!
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: I can't bear to see Rhodes Island sacrifice anyone!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Think about our goal! Think about what we came here for!
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: This isn't the time to talk about that still!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: --? The heat... is concentrating in her hands?
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: Is she... distorting the space around her?
attributes.name: Guard

attributes.content: No, that's... the superheated air around her!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: Watch out! She's getting ready to use her Arts...
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: No... You can't! Nearl!! Come back, now!!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: That's not her... You'll be killed if you--
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: *cough*... Stay back! Don't worry about me...
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: What are you saying... don't worry?
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: You don't have a single intact piece of armor on you, and you're telling me not to worry? !
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Nearl! You stubborn son of a...!
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: ... Invisible flames just swept over our head.
attributes.name: Ace

attributes.content: Fall back. This entire block is melting...
attributes.name: Ace

attributes.content: Just what monstrosity am I fighting against?
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: We have to interrupt her casting somehow...
attributes.name: Ace

attributes.content: Snipers, take aim at the enemy!
attributes.name: Ace

attributes.content: Resistance will usher hope into this land.
attributes.name: Talulah

attributes.content: But resistance... will not change your fate.
attributes.name: Talulah

attributes.content: Our work here is done, and your group has proven to be quite interesting.
attributes.name: Talulah

attributes.content: However, that is all you are worth.
attributes.name: Talulah

attributes.content: Rhodes Island, you should have stood firmly with the Infected.
attributes.name: Talulah

attributes.content: Why is the entire plaza... getting scorched?
attributes.name: Medic

attributes.content: I... I can't breathe... it burns...
attributes.name: Medic

attributes.content: In a heartbeat... every object around her has been reduced to nothingness...
attributes.name: Guard

attributes.content: You have the resilience of liberators.
attributes.name: Talulah

attributes.content: Amiya. You know what must be done.
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: This is the price you must pay for slaughtering your fellow Infected.
attributes.name: Talulah

attributes.content: I shall grant you an ending that I am quite fond of.
attributes.name: Talulah

attributes.content: That amount of heat, at such a scale... No, no!
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Protect Amiya and the Doctor! Quick!!
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: I will never... allow you to do that!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Amiya is holding back the enemy's Arts... all by herself...?
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: It's no good... That power is too tremendous!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: Even Amiya won't be able to...
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: She won't be able to hold out for long!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: Don't worry... Don't worry about me...
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: I want to... I must... protect you all!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Dark matter... is sealing the enemy's Arts within the plaza...
attributes.name: Medic

attributes.content: H-her barrier is catching on fire!
attributes.name: Guard

attributes.content: Even if this brings disaster, even if I...!
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: I don't want to lose... the person dearest to me... ever again...
attributes.name: Amiya

attributes.content: Damn it... We're going to lose her...!
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: ... 'O Light of Kazimierz, the Radiant Knight offers her body to thee...'
attributes.name: Nearl

attributes.content: Doctor! Just go! We'll help Amiya, but you have to...
attributes.name: Dobermann

attributes.content: Dobermann, take her with you. I'll see you soon.
attributes.name: Ace

attributes.content: I'm sorry, Dr {@nickname}. You might not remember me.
attributes.name: Ace

attributes.content: But I remember you, and I know what kind of person you are.
attributes.name: Ace

attributes.content: ... There will come a day when you and Amiya will face this cruel land together.
attributes.name: Ace

attributes.content: That is why... you must cherish her, Doctor.
attributes.name: Ace
